short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The PUBLIQ extension enables to import and to generate wallet addresses, to transfers funds between wallets.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The PUBLIQ extension enables to import and to generate wallet addresses, to transfers funds between wallets, and to see the details of the transactions.
